@NODE "The Med" "The Med"
@NEXT "About me"
@PREV "MAIN"
@TOC "MAIN"

   @{U}The Med:@{UU}

   It“s a 10-channel Stereo OctaMEDSoundstudio Med. The most samples are by me.
   A few of Samples are from other ProTracker Mods.
   If you want, you can remix it. You can also use the amples.
   For playing in high-quality chose the 68020-icon.If you have a slower machine
   chose the 68000-icon.
   Enjoy the Music and good luck.
@ENDNODE

